title: 4 Rare 80s Albums [Part 154] New Wave
description:
I hope you guys and gals enjoyed the previous post (vol. 153) and that you're ready for more cool music. Let's add some more obscure and hard to find albums to this huge 80s archive. For vol. 154, we have:


Perfect Zebras - Zebra [1983]

The Lost Tropics - The Lost Tropics [1983]

The Stars That Wouldn't Shine - The Stars That Wouldn't Shine [1983]

West And Byrd - West & Byrd (Comateens) [1988]
